Subject: [PATCH v2 21/62] bnx2x: add TSO support for SIT tunnels
Patch-mainline: v3.13-rc1
Git-commit: 2e3bd6a40865a7da486eaa36bb52a781bd70f5a1
References: bnc#853494 FATE#315918

bnx2x driver already handles TSO for GRE and IPIP, current code
is the same for SIT.

